    "name": "The Questness: Light of Ra",
    "steam_appid": 3289250,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this exciting game, you become an Egyptologist named Nora, who came to Egypt to do her favorite thing - explore ancient buildings and study the mythology of antiquity together with her colleague.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They discover incredible buildings that amaze their imagination. These ruins are not marked on any map, guidebook, or scientific references.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But soon armed people appear on the horizon. Who are they? Bandits? Local tribes? Or wandering criminals?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289250/extras/4edf89d8a07da9db55060ca048cb47dd.poster.avif?t=1759953291\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289250/extras/4edf89d8a07da9db55060ca048cb47dd.webm?t=1759953291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289250/extras/4edf89d8a07da9db55060ca048cb47dd.mp4?t=1759953291\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have to find out the secrets of this place, which is full of traps that lie in wait for you at every step, where you need to be extremely careful to survive in this place kept for eternity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289250/extras/2a340d0b2ea4c9fb50d5b6b33bb020dc.poster.avif?t=1759953291\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289250/extras/2a340d0b2ea4c9fb50d5b6b33bb020dc.webm?t=1759953291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289250/extras/2a340d0b2ea4c9fb50d5b6b33bb020dc.mp4?t=1759953291\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch your every step, listen to every rustle that the walls make - your life will depend on it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289250/extras/a25159fd45f9021d9374251449e61c8f.poster.avif?t=1759953291\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289250/extras/a25159fd45f9021d9374251449e61c8f.webm?t=1759953291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289250/extras/a25159fd45f9021d9374251449e61c8f.mp4?t=1759953291\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Using all your professional skills, you will have to study the stories that the hieroglyphs of these places hide, read ancient texts, study and translate them... and also gain new knowledge and information - which will help you to delve deeper into the secrets and history of this world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289250/extras/e53661d6921876eb56db32aac85dbae7.poster.avif?t=1759953291\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289250/extras/e53661d6921876eb56db32aac85dbae7.webm?t=1759953291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289250/extras/e53661d6921876eb56db32aac85dbae7.mp4?t=1759953291\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow the beam of light that will lead you along the path of history - perhaps the gods of antiquity themselves are helping you to walk this path!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289250/extras/6fc074a4f12b0e1406ec4341c1f82637.poster.avif?t=1759953291\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289250/extras/6fc074a4f12b0e1406ec4341c1f82637.webm?t=1759953291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289250/extras/6fc074a4f12b0e1406ec4341c1f82637.mp4?t=1759953291\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will also have to plunge into the stories of ordinary people who visited these places and remained there forever as prisoners of darkness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289250/extras/dcb655f83661af6145cd20879037563a.poster.avif?t=1759953291\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289250/extras/dcb655f83661af6145cd20879037563a.webm?t=1759953291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289250/extras/dcb655f83661af6145cd20879037563a.mp4?t=1759953291\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your things as well as those objects that you can discover and find - you will have to create, as well as combine things and devices that will help you pass these tests.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289250/extras/1e53c1d028fc0a2dd030d257dfb67bf5.poster.avif?t=1759953291\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289250/extras/1e53c1d028fc0a2dd030d257dfb67bf5.webm?t=1759953291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>To get out or to remain in the darkness forever - it's up to you, everything depends only on you...</strong></p>",
